                <desc>At the initial stage of this publication, translation will be given only of
                    the recognised fragment of Demetrios of Skepsis.</desc>
                <p>From Scepsis comes also Demetrios, who we mention often, the scholar who
                    explained the Trojan Catalogue and who was born at about the same time as Crates
                    and Aristarchus</p> </div>

